84
00:03:05,850 --> 00:03:07,750
People would say, "Hey,
it's good to see you.

85
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:09,660
What have you been up to lately?"

86
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:11,790
Life is full of activities.

87
00:03:11,790 --> 00:03:14,090
People have hobbies, people have jobs.

88
00:03:14,090 --> 00:03:16,440
There are things that people do every day

89
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:18,520
and sometimes those things change.

90
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:21,770
So it was really fun to be
able to ask this question.

91
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:24,470
And it was fun that people
asked me this question,

92
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:25,840
because then you can talk about

93
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:28,040
the new things that
you've been doing lately.

94
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,257
So the third question you can ask,

95
00:03:30,257 --> 00:03:32,180
"What have you been up to lately?"

96
