What have you been up to lately?

100
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,680
That's how I would say it at normal speed.

101
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,670
What have you been up to lately?

102
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:46,360
The fourth question you can
ask is, "How are things?"

103
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,910
That's kind of the short version.

104
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:49,580
You could say, "So, how are things?"

105
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:51,840
Or, "So how are things with you?"

106
