said, "How's the new truck?"

133
00:04:57,700 --> 00:05:01,750
So you can combine how with is
to make the contraction how's

134
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:03,810
and ask questions about things

135
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:05,280
you already know a little bit about,

136
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,990
but you want to know more.

137
00:05:06,990 --> 00:05:10,240
A sixth way to ask questions
during an English conversation

138
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,710
